diffs.og:
Project General Facts
Amra Residences sets a new standard for wellness-inspired living, seamlessly combining hospitality and holistic design in three elegant sea-facing towers in Umm Al Quwain. The project was developed with a focus on balance and longevity, reflecting an architectural philosophy centered on tranquility, sustainability, and a connection to nature. Each building blends harmoniously with the surrounding lagoon and mangroves, creating an environment where serenity and sophistication coexist.

Residents are welcomed into a refined sanctuary designed around the principles of integrative wellness. Each apartment comes fully furnished and serviced, featuring spacious balconies, biophilic interiors, and a calming palette of natural materials. The thoughtful design promotes well-being while providing flexibility for both permanent residents and those seeking a reprieve from the fast pace of modern life. With interiors curated by renowned design studios such as 1508 London, TRUSH Design, and Design Nomad, Amra showcases a global collaboration of craftsmanship and innovation.

The project's amenities redefine resort-style living, offering over 100 facilities dedicated to wellness, leisure, and social connection. Residents can indulge in infinity pools with views of the lagoon, a cutting-edge gym, yoga and pilates studios, spa areas, organic dining options, and private beach clubs. In addition to physical wellness, Amra nurtures emotional and intellectual harmony through art galleries, co-working spaces, and areas for meditation and community gatherings — creating a holistic ecosystem for the body, mind, and spirit.

Finishing and Materials
Modern finishes using high-quality materials.

Kitchen and Appliances
Fully equipped kitchens.

Furnishing
Fully furnished.

Location Description and Benefits
Umm Al Quwain, one of the UAE's most serene emirates, offers a unique blend of tranquility and opportunity. Away from the hustle and bustle of city life, it provides a peaceful coastal lifestyle with pristine beaches, crystal-clear waters, and lush mangroves that form a natural retreat. The emirate’s appeal lies in its simplicity and authenticity, offering residents a slower pace of life without compromising on modern comforts.

Beyond its natural splendor, Umm Al Quwain is quickly becoming a center for sustainable and wellness-focused living. The emirate’s leadership is investing in eco-friendly developments, cultural preservation, and infrastructure that promotes well-being and community engagement. Its proximity — just a short drive from Dubai and Sharjah — allows residents to enjoy both the peace of nature and easy access to the UAE's major business and leisure destinations.

For those seeking harmony, Umm Al Quwain offers a rare blend of heritage and modernity. With its expanding hospitality sector, marinas, and family-friendly attractions, it is becoming a destination for those who prioritize mindfulness, security, and a strong sense of belonging. Living here means embracing a lifestyle characterized by peace, space, and the timeless beauty of the Arabian Gulf.
